{
  "stem": "10835.3",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'43.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At the beginning of 1944, we-- our camp received the transport of Hungarian women who came to us wearing just a pair of shoes and a dress, nothing at-- else at all, no, underwear, no coats, no nothing.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And their heads were shaved.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And that was a time when Hungary was actually an ally of Germany for a while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But then Germany occupied them.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they deported the Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the funny thing is that some of these women, were either they were converted to Christianity and some of them were ultra-orthodox.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And they were brought out camp.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And they told us what had happened to them.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then-- I think it must've been March of 1944-- when one night, Mengele and two other probably doctors, too, or officers came to our building, to our-- to our factory, the-- actually to our camp.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And they locate-- they locate themselves in the office of our secretary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "They drew a circle in chalk.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It must've been like, oh, 30 inches in diameter.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And they made us strip all the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And we all had to step into that circle and turn front and back to-- to these three people.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And after seeing us, we were given a number on a string.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I received a number which was a little disk on a-- on a string-- 21,173, that was the number that I received-- and dismissed.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Once you received a number, you kind of felt at ease.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Because some people didn't.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And those people were-- were set to be ready to-- to be deported to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Of course, there was plenty crying and screaming.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "Because there was a mother and a daughter where the daughter received a number and the mother didn't.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
